# Release Process

## Version bump (all together)
1. `PAGE_VERSION` in `index.html` → e.g. `2026-07-03-v22`
2. `version.json` → `{ "build": "...", "label": "v22" }`
3. `refresh.html` → `?b=22` in redirect
4. `<head>` cache script → `b=22` check
5. `Copy-Item index.html hospital-bills.html -Force`

## Deploy
```powershell
git add index.html hospital-bills.html version.json refresh.html [others]
git commit -m "Description (v22)."
git push origin main
```
GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/pages.yml`) deploys automatically.

## Live URL (never change for family)
https://tevskrishna.github.io/hospital-bills/

## Cache stuck
Direct family to: `/refresh.html`

## Commits
Only when user explicitly requests.

## Pre-release checklist
- [ ] Version numbers aligned (4 places)
- [ ] `hospital-bills.html` synced
- [ ] `CHANGELOG.md` updated
- [ ] No secrets in diff
- [ ] Regression checklist passed (see testing.mdc)

## PWA
Update `manifest.json` `theme_color` / `background_color` only when brand colors change.
